These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, asparagus, blueberry, garlic
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, lizard, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, swimming, handball, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the owner of the cat##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the far left##1
4. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the ferret is between the person who's sport is handball and the person eating asparagus##2
6. the person who's sport is swimming is the owner of the lizard##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | blueberry | garlic  | asparagus | artichoke  |
| Pet         | turtle    | ferret  | cat       | lizard     |
| Sport   | handball     | soccer | biathlon       | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, drawing, magic-tricks, reading
City: rome, san-francisco, paris, boston
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, surfing, swimming
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person traveling to boston and the person who's hobby is reading##2
5. the person traveling to boston is the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
7. the person traveling to paris is the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | drawing | chess    | reading  | magic-tricks |
| City   | boston  | rome  | san-francisco   | paris    |
| Sport         | sailing | swimming | climbing | surfing      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, sprite, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, trike, tram, subway
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, folk, house, indie
1. the fan of folk is between the fan of indie and the person drinking mirinda##2
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
6. the fan of country is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the fan of house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | tea         | lemonade   | sprite    |
| Transport         | trike | subway | boat | tram |
| Music-Genre   | house   | folk        | indie      | country   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, dutch, german, polish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, skateboarding, tennis
House: modern, palace, ranch-style, colonial
1. the ranch-style house is on the far left##1
2. the modern house is between the colonial house and the polish##2
3. the german is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the modern house is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the german is on the right of the australian##1
6. the colonial house is between the person who's sport is cricket and the palace house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | polish        | dutch   | australian | german |
| Sport         | skateboarding | cricket | cycling    | tennis |
| House     | ranch-style       | modern     | colonial       | palace    |

