.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, garlic, raspberry, strawberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, puzzles, reading
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, may, april, march
1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is the person eating garlic##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person eating strawberry##2
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | strawberry  | raspberry | eggplant | garlic     |
| Hobby   | board-games | puzzles   | reading  | camping    |
| Birthday     | may        | march       | february      | april |

