.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
4 different games are played: bridge, backgammon, scrabble, poker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, fantasy, romance, time-travel
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, ship, trike
1. the person watching disaster movies is the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the ship is the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the bus is between the person watching romance movies and the person playing scrabble##2
6. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the bus is the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Game           | backgammon | poker | scrabble    | bridge   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance      | fantasy   | time-travel | disaster |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus       | ship        | trike    |

